snippet.title: ASCAPE - Trailer
snippet.description:
I N F O

I'm super hyped about my first little video game. I had lots of fun with this small project. The game will be released on 1.1.2023 and I hope I don't have to postpone it. When the game is finished, it will be uploaded to the MEGA folder. The probability is also very high that a video in German will appear of this game on my channel. Until then, Merry Christmas to all of you!

T R A I L E R    M U S I C

J.S.Bach Concerto no.1 in D Minor BWV 1052

T H E   L I N K
